 PlayStation 高管表示《Palworld》可能会登陆 PS5 https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-could-be-coming-to-ps5-suggests-playstation-exec-3576198?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=palworld-could-be-coming- to-ps5-建议-playstation-execRyan Easby Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:31:02 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS5Video Game CultureXbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3576198 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="“Palworld”信用：Pocketpair" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该游戏于上周推出抢先体验</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-could-be-coming-to-ps5-suggests-playstation-exec-3576198">PlayStation 高管表示，《Palworld》的帖子可能会登陆 PS5，</a>最先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="“Palworld”信用：Pocketpair" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/palworld-ancient-technology-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据 PlayStation 独立开发者 Shuhei Yoshida 在 X（以前的 Twitter）上发布的帖子， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/palworld">Palworld</a></em>可能很快就会登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation">PlayStation</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/persona-3-reload-preview-interview-3571048">《女神异闻录 3：重装版》将成为必玩重制版</a></strong></li></ul><p>吉田回复了一个<a href="https://twitter.com/boat_233/status/1748602328603890089" target="_blank" rel="noopener">帖子</a>，要求团队“支持SIE [<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony-interactive-entertainment">索尼互动娱乐</a>]，以便PS5版本能够尽快发布”。</p><p>吉田在<a href="https://twitter.com/yosp/status/1748615687616999769" target="_blank" rel="noopener">回复</a>中标记了 PlayStation 的开发合作伙伴，并写着“是”。</p><p>此前， <em>Palworld</em>的社区经理发帖表示，该游戏“不会在 PlayStation 上发布”，只会在“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox">Xbox</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a> ”上提供。然而，1 月 21 日，社区经理在<a href="https://twitter.com/Bucky_cm/status/1749054941849915398?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1749054941849915398%7Ctwgr%5Ed7d0760509b98d37e71dc5e515cd585cbb6afa9a%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurogamer.net%2Fplaystation-eyeing-up-palworld-head-of-indies-shuhei-yoshida-suggests" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a>上发帖表示， <em>Palworld</em>仍可能登陆 PlayStation。 </p><figure id="attachment_3492258" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3492258" style="width: 1252px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3492258" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/palworld-qa-with-pocketpair-inc-2.jpg" alt="" width="1252" height="795" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/20