de-squad-kill-the-justice-league">《自杀小队：杀死正义联盟》</a></em>开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/rocksteady-studios">Rocksteady</a>宣布了游戏的发布后计划，其中包括一个<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-will-feature-a-playable-joker-3575573">可玩的平行宇宙小丑</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-could-be-coming-to-ps5-suggests-playstation-exec-3576198">PlayStation 高管表示，《Palworld》的帖子可能会登陆 PS5，</a>最先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
